@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api

### Get All Books
GET {{baseUrl}}/books

### Get Book by ID
# Replace with actual UUID after creating a book
GET {{baseUrl}}/books/{{bookId}}

### Create a Book
POST {{baseUrl}}/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Way of Kings",
  "author": "Brandon Sanderson",
  "description": "The first book in The Stormlight Archive series.",
  "coverImageUrl": "https://example.com/way-of-kings.jpg"
}

